Name: Time elapsed from Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation to SW-EIC Reject in variants ending with SW-EIC Reject

Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completed' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity SW-Initial Reviewer Selection and activity SW-EIC Reject for cases where activity SW-EIC Reject occurs

Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Minimum time for SW-EIC Reject when preceded directly by SW-Awaiting EIC Decision without any intermediate reviewer activities
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'
